<c74object name='av.pix.mask' category='' module=''>

    <digest>
        Create a black/white mask from an image
    </digest>

    <description>
        Create a black/white mask from an incoming texture based on a specified range. Use either brightness or hue for the range-test to create the mask. Also generates an alpha channel for the mask to be combined with blending in a layer.
    </description>
    
    <discussion>
        
    </discussion>

